Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:03.08,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.52,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.99,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.99,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case involves a missing corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.25,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even if you do deceive everybody,\Nthere's still always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is quiet around here lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:10.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys can't do\Nanything if nobody needs help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If clients showed up that easily,\Nwe detectives would be worry-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dr. Agasa went through the trouble\Nof making badges for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They look cool no matter\Nhow many times I look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Detective Boys"... Our exclusive design!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They even act as transceivers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:31.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah! These badges are worthless\Nif we have no cases to solve—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:36.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a small request for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Hiroki, from the next classroom over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? A murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fraud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents are having an affair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:49.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Akira disappeared last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A missing persons case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapping isn't out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does she look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:02.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a picture of her. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it was this cat that disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad it wasn't a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pay you each 10 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:16.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:20.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We only handle higher-level cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the cat will come back eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to give you some\NKamen Yaiba cards if you found her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See! I collect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamen Yaiba cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, these are the super rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:47.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hyper Golden Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We accept the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, we can't find her anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:18.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange—she disappeared\Nyesterday, so she should still be nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:23.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. We worked really hard,\Nso give us our cards now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You didn't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:30.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, does this cat have any habits\Nor special abilities or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Akira's meow\Nis a lot different than other cats'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From that house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to help her right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No! This cat is uninjured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us, Conan! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have to call the police right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who made the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really see a corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:06.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, nobody has left the house\Nsince we discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the corpse is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the racket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These kids say they saw\Na dead body in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're certain we saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was lying in the bathtub, covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:36.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! I was just taking a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself! It's that room straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! The body is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See! No corpses! These brats are\Nprobably just pulling a prank on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:00.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we really saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:03.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a dead body, covered in\Nblood and lying in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy must've hidden it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately 15 minutes have\Npassed from the time you called us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until we arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:20.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough time to hide a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Search all you want! I'm going upstairs to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind if we search without you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ransack the place if you want,\Nthere's nothing to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:37.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any problems,\Ntell my brother. He'll be home soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the police must be bored to death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if they'll make a fuss over\Na bunch of deviant little miscreants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Search! The body's here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Search every nook and cranny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the body at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The younger brother has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:13.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:18.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This lad here says he saw a corpse in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A corpse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:25.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's alright! It wasn't worth much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:35.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Keep it down, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it my brother is upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He seems rather angry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my rudeness, but what exactly\Ndoes your brother do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a writer, for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, he usually stays\Nat home and does nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my card...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomofumi Tanaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you work for a securities firm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So just you and your brother live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though technically it's my house.\NMy brother lives here for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A leaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've checked the house\Nfrom top to bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is your brother's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:27.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I hope he doesn't get too mad at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:29.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:36.83,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...the high pressure ridge will bring clear skies to most of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. It looks like he's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:45.51,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...showers starting at around 1 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.91,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The rain may remain heavy until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:51.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There's a large tree in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:10:00.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! If you're going to sleep,\Nat least turn the TV off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like he heard me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:06.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I've shown you everything I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:09.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And no dead bodies whatsoever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You little scoundrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:19.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, the body could've been\Ncarried outside by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:30.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say no one entered or\Nleft this house before we arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I only watched from the\Nphone booth in front of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:42.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a high wall behind the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you saw that big tree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tied a body to yourself and used that tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:50.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you could get over the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka residence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you must have the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:57.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong number. So what were\Nwe talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The tree in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:10.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was originally there\Nwhen I bought the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:14.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was the ringer off on that phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you alright up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you climb over it with someone tied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get down; the outer side\Nof the wall is an embankment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any footholds or anything of the sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a walkway about 40 centimeters wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it would be impossible\Nto use with a body tied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:41.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I could get down, it would\Ntake everything I had just to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no corpse inside the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's impossible to carry one outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We really saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you did catch that gang of Italian thieves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it was still stupid of me to trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How could the body have vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:22.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All I can think of at this point is that\Nthe older brother washed the blood off
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:27.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}while the younger brother made\Npreparations to carry the body out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like the leaf that was\Non the younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:42.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that they really did\Nuse this tree to get the body outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here? Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:55.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them call our\Ndetective club a bunch of liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}These guys can be such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:06.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That scary man's still sleeping there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:11.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, he should at least close\Nthe curtain or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:16.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And doesn't he ever get tired sleeping like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:21.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Have I been looking at this\Nthe wrong way the whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:41.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've figured out the trick\Nthe killer used to hide the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:45.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here. I'm going inside to see if I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! We'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:52.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There may be a killer inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go wait by the phone booth outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you if I find the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, it's your job to contact the police right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He locked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:08.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now for the room upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This isn't good—he's still awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What did he put down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! That trick could work if you used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've got most of this case figured out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan sure is taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:38.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd contact us using\Nthese miniature transceivers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if he found the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:43.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he's actually trying to\Ntake all the credit for himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see! So I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:06.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's an answering machine\Nand a VCR in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:18.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard something in here.\NMust've been my imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's taking so long, Conan?\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like he's been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of there, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give yourself up and come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:39.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Dammit! I guess I have no choice now\Nbut to leave my transmitter on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:43.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should give yourself up, Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither we nor the police could find the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:50.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was in the house the entire time,\Nright under our noses, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:51.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse I'm referring to is the man\Nwho was sitting in this very room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,watching television—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,—your older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how your trick worked...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that we had discovered your brother's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you washed all the blood off him in the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,put a bathrobe on him,\Nsat him in a chair upstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:26.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then came down to talk to the police,\Nwho had come in search of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:30.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You had boldly disguised yourself\Nas the brother you murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you have always looked similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Relatives would know the difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but everybody else would be fooled\Nby such a simple disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, while the police searched the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you jumped from the 2nd floor window\Nto the tree, and then over the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The outer side of the wall\Nacts as an embankment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was just enough room\Nfor a single person to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You then returned to the front\Ndoor as the younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:57.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and acted like you had\Nno idea what had happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You found the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The younger brother was the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the older brother\Nwho was sleeping was the corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous. He was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned the TV off when his brother told him to,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:18.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he even yelled at you\Nwhen you broke that jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:24.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You tried to make it look\Nlike your brother was really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you used the VCR, the answering machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:30.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and your cell phone to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That shouting was something you had\Nrecorded to the answering machine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before the police showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You played it back on the answering machine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by using your cell phone's quick-dial feature at just the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you turned off the\Nringers on all the phones in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it sound like your brother was yelling from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:56.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Keep it down, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of this fact, you picked up\Nthe phone—which didn't ring—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when a person calling the wrong number\Njust happened to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:06.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably saw the light on the phone\Nblink when the phone call came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:09.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't picked it up, the\Nanswering machine would've kicked in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:14.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we would have heard him yelling again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:23.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Keep it down, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:28.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The TV turned off because you\Nset the VCR's timer in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then did a little bit of acting of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Tomofumi Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:38.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Something bad might happen\Nto Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} if you don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, will you? I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.91,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You're one smart kid, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:47.42,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:51.15,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I killed my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being taken advantage of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:16.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By my worthless brother, who stayed\Nin my house and refused to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:20.75,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I found these documents in your room, Tomofumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.05,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}These are illegally-traded stocks, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:29.56,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't worry. We're brothers. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:34.00,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But in return, you'll take care of me\Nfor the rest of my life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took care of him ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:41.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then he demanded\Neven more money from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:47.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I bashed that parasite's head in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:53.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Little brat! There's no way for you\Nto understand how I felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:56.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved my brother more than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:03.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My talented brother, who was\Nprized as a rising new novelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:08.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's disguised as his older brother!\NHe's really gone insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:14.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I idolized my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:19.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to be like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then he fell from grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:27.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The brother I idolized so much\Nhad become a common leech!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:31.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking back that brother who I looked up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:38.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you get it? I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:41.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...going to become my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use these Power Kick Shoes to finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! My kicks are so strong\Nthat they destroy these vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've seen through\Nmy trick, I can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, kid! Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:07.59,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The authorities arrived shortly afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:10.80,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The inspector's faith in us\Nwas restored once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:14.90,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and the case that started as a "missing cats"\Ninvestigation came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.33,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No clients as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:27.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, not even catching\Na murderer seems to have helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:28.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My cat disappeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:37.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this may be tied to another incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:40.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's no ordinary cat, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's take the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Besides, we have nothing else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:48.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We found out later that Hiroki's\Ncat Akira was nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:51.14,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}than a mischievous cat who liked\Nto sneak into all kinds of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:55.30,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She never led us to any further incidents.
